Printcare Gains in Colombo After Stock-Split, Dividend Offers

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e
-- 
2011-04-21T05:02:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-21/printcare-gains-in-colombo-after-stock-split-dividend-offers.html
Printcare Plc (CARE)  rose to a 52-week
high in Colombo trading after saying it plans to divide each
stock into five. Separately, the company said it will pay a
final dividend of 2.50 rupees a share.  Printcare rose as much as 33 percent and was trading 21
percent higher at 318 rupees at 10:17 a.m. local time.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
